49
00:03:04,800 --> 00:03:06,600
I like the drawing and everything,

50
00:03:06,600 --> 00:03:08,120
but the romance part stinks.

51
00:03:08,840 --> 00:03:11,240
Those two have been through everything

52
00:03:11,240 --> 00:03:12,640
