94
00:05:03,320 --> 00:05:04,840
So I’ve arranged that

95
00:05:04,840 --> 00:05:05,680
since the very beginning.

96
00:05:05,680 --> 00:05:08,120
I call it Wrestling Love.

97
00:05:08,120 --> 00:05:09,720
Wrestling my foot!

98
00:05:10,600 --> 00:05:12,160
