134
00:06:22,040 --> 00:06:22,360
But...

135
00:06:22,360 --> 00:06:22,880
No buts.

136
00:06:23,720 --> 00:06:24,640
5 pm tomorrow.

137
00:06:24,640 --> 00:06:26,160
Hand in your new design
of the male character.

138
00:06:27,040 --> 00:06:28,240
If I see another muscle man,

139
00:06:29,240 --> 00:06:31,640
