140
00:06:31,640 --> 00:06:32,800
Got it, got it. Ouch!

141
00:06:32,800 --> 00:06:34,270
Ow…!

142
00:06:44,360 --> 00:06:47,240
You... You’ve never felt
your heart racing?

143
00:06:48,840 --> 00:06:51,480
Heart racing, aside from
the abstract meaning,

144
00:06:51,480 --> 00:06:53,360
