I’ll be in trouble.

149
00:07:11,040 --> 00:07:11,800
Beef jerky.

150
00:07:23,360 --> 00:07:24,720
Where’s your owner?

151
00:07:25,760 --> 00:07:26,720
Do you want this?

152
00:07:32,120 --> 00:07:32,640
So adorable.

153
00:07:36,120 --> 00:07:37,400
Qi Bao.

154
00:07:38,240 --> 00:07:40,280
I’m also surnamed Qi,

155
00:07:40,280 --> 00:07:41,800
so we’re sort of family.

156
00:07:44,920 --> 00:07:46,920
Are you asking me to
help you find your owner?

157
00:07:49,560 --> 00:07:50,040
Fine.

158
00:07:50,720 --> 00:07:53,640
I have no inspiration anyway.

159
00:07:53,640 --> 00:07:56,480
It’s better to take you home.

160
00:07:57,040 --> 00:07:57,640
Finished.

161
00:08:00,080 --> 00:08:00,960
Let’s go.

162
00:08:06,120 --> 00:08:08,200
Qi Bao. Qi Bao. Qi Bao!

163
00:08:08,620 --> 00:08:10,180
(Red Joy)

164
00:08:13,760 --> 00:08:14,440
Qi Bao!

165
00:08:15,560 --> 00:08:16,920
