207
00:11:12,080 --> 00:11:12,640
Excuse me.

208
00:11:17,000 --> 00:11:18,480
I don’t care where you are.
Get your ass back.

209
00:11:18,480 --> 00:11:19,240
ASAP!

210
00:11:20,760 --> 00:11:21,600
